This is for
<a href=\"https://github.com/ibpsa/modelica-ibpsa/issues/303\">issue 303</a>.
</li>
<li>
April 14, 2008, by Michael Wetter:<br/>
First implementation.
</li>
</ul>
</html>"));
end RegNonZeroPowerDerivative_2_Check;
